1. *Spavao* je već od 16h. (He was sleeping since 4pm.)
2. Ona je *spavala* u pola 7. (She was sleeping at half past 6.)
3. *Spavao* bi malo preko podneva. (He would sleep a little bit past noon.)
4. *Spavale* su do 10h. (They were sleeping until 10am.)
5. *Spavati* će nekoliko sati. (He will sleep for a few hours.)